# Build outputs
release
.electron-cache
build/
# docs 目录只忽略非图片文件，图片保留在仓库中
docs/*
!docs/*.png
!docs/*.jpg
!docs/*.jpeg
!docs/*.gif
!docs/*.svg
!docs/*.webp

# 忽略本地设计规格文档目录，避免 specs 和 superpowers/specs 上传到仓库。
specs/
**/specs/
docs/superpowers/specs/
superpowers/specs/
**/superpowers/specs/
.superpowers/

# Private API keys (local only, packed into release builds by electron-builder)
electron/api-keys.cjs

# VIP license generator (local only, contains private key)
tools/
tools/license-generator.cjs
tools/private-key.pem
*.pem
vip-license.cjs

